Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:01.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone, I'm a netizen who has been lurking online for over a decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.34,0:00:06.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I'm known as Pashoushusheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:08.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,The reason I've surfaced today is quite unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:09.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,It's because
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:14.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I've recently been honored to be at the center of a controversy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:19.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,And yet, I've somehow managed to come out of it unscathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:21.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I feel a bit like I've survived a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:24.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,As a loyal audience member of both parties involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:27.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I've witnessed the entire controversy unfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.41,0:00:30.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I hope to provide an objective account of the events
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:32.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,for those who are unclear about the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.64,0:00:35.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,As the saying goes, understanding the cause and effect
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.67,0:00:38.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,is essential to determine who is right or wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:40.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and most importantly, what we should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:41.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Finally,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:44.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I also want to share some thoughts I've kept in my heart for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.11,0:00:44.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Please hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:48.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:51.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,First, let me briefly introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:53.41,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:55.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,On Tieba and Weibo, my ID is Xuanwuyisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.77,0:00:59.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I've been a viewer of Luo Xiaohei for over a decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.57,0:01:02.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Their spin-off comic, Lanxi Town,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:04.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,transitioned to a paid model for the last three episodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:06.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,To this day, I've purchased every episode without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.84,0:01:11.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I've also bought their physical books.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:13.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I'm also one of the earliest followers of Black Myth: Wukong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:17.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,When they opened pre-orders recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:19.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I immediately purchased their physical deluxe edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:22.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,And I pre-ordered the digital standard edition on PS5.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:27.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Regarding this controversy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:29.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,it started with the main artist of Luo Xiaohei's spin-off comic, Lanxi Town,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.93,0:01:32.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Sun Gua,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:34.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,who reposted rumors about the main creators of Black Myth: Wukong on Weibo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:39.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,She accused the early promotion of Black Myth: Wukong of insulting women,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.01,0:01:42.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but then frantically whitewashing before its release.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:45.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I had seen this Douban post a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:48.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,It's full of distortions and lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:50.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,truly malicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:51.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'll explain in detail later
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:53.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,how this post spreads rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:55.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,But for the sake of narrative,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:57.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I'll put it aside for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.23,0:01:58.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,So, I pointed out in the comments,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:02:00.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,to carefully look at the so-called evidence in the post.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:03.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to accuse Game Science so maliciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:06.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Vulgarity is vulgarity,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:08.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but you can't forcefully label them as insulting women.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:09.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Game Science,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:11.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,is vulgar, but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:14.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,you can't forcefully label them as insulting women.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:15.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,As soon as my comment was posted,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:17.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,some people started mocking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:19.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,For those who weren't too excessive,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:21.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I made some slightly sarcastic responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:23.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,But after a few exchanges,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:26.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,they started cursing at me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:27.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,very viciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:29.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Since there was no reasoning with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:31.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I could only choose to respect others' fate, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:34.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Sun Gua's response.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:36.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,But then I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:39.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I've been following Luo Xiaohei for so many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:41.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I don't know what kind of character their company has.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:43.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Their employees also joke around with each other on Weibo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:43.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,sometimes even drawing some erotic pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,How could they believe such baseless rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:48.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Sure enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:50.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I flipped through Sun Gua's photo album a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:53.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and found two erotic pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:03:01.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,After looking at them a few times,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:03.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I posted these two pictures in the comment section.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:06.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,And I tried to make up for Sun Gua,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:09.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,asking if she had been hacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Such an open person before,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:12.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,how could she believe such baseless rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:15.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Sure enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:16.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,someone came to over-interpret me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:18.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I responded a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:20.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but at this time, Sun Gua seemed to have finished work,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:23.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and as expected, she started to get angry at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:25.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Because her temper was always bad before,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:28.02,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I hadn't said a few words to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and I was blocked by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:31.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Now, those who cursed me in that comment section,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:33.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and those who reposted to curse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:36.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I couldn't retort anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:37.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I could only shrug,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and do my own thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:40.93,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,This matter passed after a few days,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:42.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and I was quite excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:45.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,After all, it was the first time I was cursed like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:46.86,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and cursed so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:49.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,But suddenly, this matter flared up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Because Luo Xiaohei is after all a classic work of Chinese 2D animation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:54.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,with an audience distributed across all sectors of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:58.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Among them, there are some who followed it since childhood and have now gradually joined the workforce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:01.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,So there are some audience members
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:04.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,who are self-media.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:07.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,They saw what Sun Gua posted on her Weibo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:09.06,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and spread this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:09.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Not only that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:13.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,they also did a little digging,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:16.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and found that in the Luo Xiaohei team,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,other creators also had some similar inappropriate remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:21.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,This matter became a bit serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:25.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,And Sun Gua's account is not a personal account,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:27.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,she has actually participated in the promotion of Luo Xiaohei,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:28.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and in her Weibo introduction,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:32.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,she has her company's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:35.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to say that during the promotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,you circle out each of your employees on Weibo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and when something happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,you just say it's a personal remark and that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:42.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,This is a bit of a double standard, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,So, everyone had to go to Sun Gua's boss
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:47.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,to demand an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:48.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Not only does Black Myth: Wukong
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:49.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,need such an explanation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but Luo Xiaohei's side must also clarify their stance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, they will also suffer a lot of adverse effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:56.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Soon, a large number of people angered by Sun Gua
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:58.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,went to find Luo Xiaohei's director, MTJJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:00.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Some of the angrier ones
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:01.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,even threatened him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:03.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,saying that they would retaliate against Luo Xiaohei
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:06.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,when promoting the second part in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:10.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Among these people, there are undoubtedly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:13.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,some who are indeed fans of Black Myth: Wukong,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:16.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but it cannot be ruled out that some are deliberately fanning the flames,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:19.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,hoping for both sides to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Under the crazy bombardment of messages,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:24.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,MTJJ posted a Weibo with over a thousand words,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:27.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,making the first wave of response.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Its main content is too long,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:33.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I'll summarize it for everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:34.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,First, it distanced itself from the rumors slandering Black Myth: Wukong,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:36.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,a bit sarcastically,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:39.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and said that what Sun Gua said were personal remarks,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,he couldn't manage them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:41.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,But under such pressure from everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:44.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,he had to criticize Sun Gua,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:46.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and asked her to shut up immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:48.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Additionally, the remarks of the main creators of Black Myth: Wukong from years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,he said were just bawdy jokes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:52.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but I feel he was a bit sarcastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:55.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,He himself admitted
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,that he had told many bawdy jokes before,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:58.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but back then, no one was stirring up trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:00.74,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,because the online atmosphere was very relaxed at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:02.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Now, if he says it again,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,he feels it's just asking for trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:06.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,And he also said,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:08.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,if being disliked for telling bawdy jokes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:10.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,then one should unconditionally bear the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:12.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Finally, perhaps out of protecting his own work,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:14.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,he was a bit scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and he sharply retaliated against
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,those who demanded an explanation from him
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:22.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and those who threatened him with Luo Xiaohei's second part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:26.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,And he even threatened to go after Game Science.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:29.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,At this time, how did Sun Gua respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:30.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,As shown in the picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:31.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,interestingly,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:36.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,later, someone found that she was a different person on Twitter,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:38.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,very patient,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:39.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,very friendly,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.72,0:06:42.31,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,very understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I don't want to make any malicious speculations about her here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:47.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I just want a sincere apology from her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:49.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,after all, she is not incapable of apologizing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:51.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,MTJJ's response,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:53.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,regardless of his sarcastic tone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:56.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,in the situation where Sun Gua was spreading rumors and was in the wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:07:00.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,he still used the Spring and Autumn Annals style to support the rumor-monger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:03.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I don't know if he was confused between right and wrong or unaware of the facts at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:07.13,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Clearly, Sun Gua's actions were detrimental to Game Science first,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:09.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but he, in the guise of a victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:12.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,threatened to go after Game Science.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:14.82,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I can't help but ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:18.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,if someone demanding an explanation from him is wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:22.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,then is it right for him to go after Game Science?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:24.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Some people even praised him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:28.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,saying he has a sense of responsibility and reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:33.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but in fact, more people were angered by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:38.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,So, a large amount of MTJJ's past misdeeds were dug up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.79,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,his bawdy jokes from back then were even more vulgar than Game Science's
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:43.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,from back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:47.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,some were clearly bawdy jokes aimed at women.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:52.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Since he thinks Game Science should be held accountable for their past remarks,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:54.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,then he should bear even greater consequences for his own more serious remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:57.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,As he said himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,he has no temper at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:02.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,The next morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:03.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,he couldn't withstand the pressure and responded again,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:07.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,saying he was too young,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:09.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,too naive,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:12.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and deserved to be targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:14.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,He also approved of Game Science's cold handling of public relations,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:17.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and gave a simple explanation for some of his own past misdeeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:20.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,He also said he would manage himself well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:23.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and focus on creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:25.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Up to this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:28.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I thought the controversy could finally come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:30.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,But someone found out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:33.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,that he quietly deleted his past misdeeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:36.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and there were also many people deliberately distorting the facts,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,inciting conflicts,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:39.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,fanning the flames,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:42.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,fanning the flames on both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:44.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,So MTJJ had to come out for the third time to make a statement,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:47.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,this time he lowered his stance even more,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:52.05,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but he still refused to directly address the root cause of the incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,that is, the rumor about Black Myth: Wukong,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the rumor reposted by Sun Gua.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:08:58.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Sun Gua also had to come out to apologize,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:02.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but while saying she would mute herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:04.57,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,she closed the comment section.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Up to this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:10.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,this incident can finally come to an end, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Some impatient netizens might be anxious,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:15.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,what rumor did Sun Gua repost?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:17.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,What's the story behind Black Myth: Wukong's own controversy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:21.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Next, I will explain this matter clearly to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:23.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,The rumor entangling Black Myth: Wukong and Game Science
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:24.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,has been around for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:28.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Every time Black Myth: Wukong trends on the hot search,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:31.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,you can see a small group of people saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:34.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Black Myth: Wukong doesn't need female players,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:37.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the main creators of Black Myth: Wukong insult women.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:42.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Although these accusations haven't affected
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:46.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the overall affirmation and expectation of the game's quality,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:50.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,every time I see these remarks, I feel a sense of frustration,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:55.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,like seeing a cockroach running in after a big cleanup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:10:00.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,If you ask them what these accusations are based on,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:04.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,they will most likely give you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:08.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,this Douban article reposted by Sun Gua.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:12.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,The so-called evidence in this article includes:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Before the predecessor of Game Science, the Douzhan Shen production team left,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:16.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,they made a self-deprecating MV,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:19.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,saying that after leaving Tencent,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,their team members would have to engage in the pornographic industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:24.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,And when Game Science was first established,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:27.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,they used self-deprecating jokes to recruit employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:30.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,When Black Myth: Wukong released its first promotional video,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:33.21,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the main planner, Feng Ji, posted on Weibo using self-deprecating jokes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:34.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and thanked everyone for their support.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:36.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,The technical artist also discussed in the Zhihu comment section
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:38.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the snake spirit NPC image in Black Myth: Wukong
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.91,0:10:40.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and briefly talked about the fetish for snake necks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.58,0:10:43.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Years ago, the main artist of Black Myth: Wukong, Yang Qi, wrote an article saying
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:49.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,they don't need female players for reverse motivation,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:53.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,reverse motivation, and the logo of Game Science looks like sperm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:54.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,After reading it, it's quite clear,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:55.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,just browse through
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:57.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the so-called evidence listed in this article,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,it's not hard to see
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:00.33,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the core members of Game Science
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:04.19,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,indeed made some remarks mixed with bawdy jokes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:06.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but without exception,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:09.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,they were all self-deprecating,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:14.90,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,never directly making vulgar jokes about any woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,This is why I said to Sun Gua,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:18.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,you can say they are vulgar,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:22.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but they have no malice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:24.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Others make self-deprecating jokes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.25,0:11:26.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and you insist on saying they are talking about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:29.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,isn't that self-inflicted humiliation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:31.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,how can you blame others?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:33.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Ah, at this point, someone might say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:36.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,what about the recruitment advertisement with "fat people die quickly"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and "forced orgasm"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:38.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I was offended.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:41.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Then I would ask you to look carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:43.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,there are many words under the picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:47.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the words are what Game Science really wants to express.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:52.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,They are just saying that Game Science highly values the health of its employees
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:56.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and encourages them to exercise,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:12:00.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and they also promote a very advanced concept,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:02.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,that is, making games,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:04.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,you must first make yourself happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:07.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,before you can release the product for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:11.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,And the so-called "no need for female players for reverse motivation",
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:15.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,does it mean they don't welcome female players to play their games?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,In fact, just carefully read
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the paragraph they excerpted in this article,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:22.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,they excerpted quite detailedly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:24.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,we can see
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:26.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,what Yang Qi actually meant here is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:30.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,he doesn't need to promote that his game has many female players
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:34.28,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,to attract those who want to pick up girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:38.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,thereby increasing the popularity and revenue of his game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:42.73,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,He is actually opposing this kind of objectification of women
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:44.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,in promotional concepts and marketing strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:48.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,He insists on using the hard power of his game to attract players,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:52.87,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,isn't this the noble pursuit of an artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,After reading it, I can only say
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:56.17,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:58.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Some people question whether Yang Qi's article
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:02.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,is promoting stereotypical views of women,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:05.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,then I would ask everyone to open their eyes and see clearly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:11.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the first paragraph here clearly states that most female players,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:14.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Yang Qi did not deny the existence of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:17.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,a small number of female players as their audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:20.53,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,he is just describing the majority situation here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:22.29,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,If it's said to this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:23.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,you still insist that he
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,is a stereotypical view,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:29.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,then I have to say you are making unreasonable accusations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:33.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,For example, I can go to the female section to see female comics,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:38.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,female players can also come to play games made for men,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:40.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,no one is stopping them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:41.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:46.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Finally, does the logo of Game Science really look like sperm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:48.43,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to everyone to judge,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:49.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I just say,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:52.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,if your mind is full of a certain thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:55.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,then you will easily see everything
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.09,0:13:56.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,as that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:58.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,And even if it is sperm, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:02.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Who isn't developed from a fertilized egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:05.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone now who is developed from an unfertilized egg
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:08.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,through parthenogenesis into a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:10.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,It doesn't exist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:12.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:16.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,those who are slandered and insulted by these rumor-mongers
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:19.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,are not only Game Science and Black Myth: Wukong,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:21.99,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,many players have also been unreasonably insulted by them,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.07,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,including me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:27.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and even some female players
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:30.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,have been viciously cursed by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:33.34,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,There's also an interesting fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:37.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Black Myth: Wukong has a Tieba,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:42.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the admin of this Tieba posted a thread at the end of last year
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:44.84,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,to debunk the rumors,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:49.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but this post did not spread beyond the Tieba,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:52.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,classic debunking, no one saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,After such a long period of continuous slander,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:56.67,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,many people have become defenders of Black Myth: Wukong,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:58.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,if you go to argue with those rumor-mongers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:00.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,you will often receive very nasty curses,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:03.14,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,for example, you can see the screenshot records above.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:06.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,So how can MTJJ say that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:09.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,if you are disliked for telling bawdy jokes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:11.69,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,there's no reason to argue,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:13.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,you can only bear it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:15.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Why so many people are extremely angry at his words,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:19.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the reason is very obvious,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,what we suffer is not just being disliked,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:24.88,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,we suffer long-term humiliation and bottomless oppression.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:29.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,It's a pity that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.36,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,our anger
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,did not vent to those rumor-mongers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:36.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but was all taken by MTJJ,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:39.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,this is really unreasonable,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:42.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,after all, seeking a hammer and getting a hammer,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.11,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and those who dug up his old accounts,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:46.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,most of them just posted what he said back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:49.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,asking if there's a problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:51.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,should it be cursed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:52.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,no one went to curse him in such a vulgar and obscene way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:54.49,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,it can be said that they gave MTJJ a lot of face,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:56.47,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but there are also some friends who noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:59.62,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:03.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,This matter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:07.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,starts with the well-known foreign game media IGN.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:10.10,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,The IGN here is the foreign IGN,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:12.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,it has a little relationship with the domestic IGN China,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:15.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but they are not subordinate to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:18.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,IGN published a media commentary,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:21.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,criticizing Game Science for insulting women,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:23.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the evidence they provided is the content in this Douban post,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:25.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and through their biased translation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:28.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,they distorted the original meaning of Yang Qi and Feng Ji,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:31.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,adding oil and vinegar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:34.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,The content of this article is very sensitive,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:37.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,so I can't post it here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:40.51,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,so I can only describe its content here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:42.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,They also said in the article
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:45.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,that they found several women who claimed to be engaged in the game industry in China,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:48.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,anonymously complaining about the gender discrimination they suffered,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:51.01,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but only their one-sided words,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:53.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,no evidence was provided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Additionally,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:59.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,this article also took the opportunity to denigrate our country's regime, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.98,0:17:03.09,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Since they want to stir the anti-China muddy water,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:07.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,don't blame me for having too many associations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:11.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Isn't it just hiring actors as witnesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:14.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,The several women they invited claimed to be engaged in the game industry in China,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:18.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,who knows where they found these extras?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:21.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Even whether they found these few people,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I have to put a question mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:28.96,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,This rumor article by foreign media, although it cannot be confirmed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:33.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the domestic rumor-mongers are indeed related to foreign forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:38.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but the content of their materials highly overlaps,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:43.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,isn't this a bit too coincidental?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:48.27,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,It's not groundless,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:50.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but a very reasonable question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:53.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:57.44,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,foreign players have been supporting Black Myth: Wukong in various ways
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:18:00.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,to express their resistance to this kind of black society forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:02.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Speaking of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:05.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the feud between Luo Xiaohei and Black Myth: Wukong,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:09.20,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I think it's basically clear,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:12.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,at least it's clear about the part I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:17.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,If you ask me what I think about this matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:21.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I just want to say that extremists should go die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:25.85,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,After all, I've been watching Luo Xiaohei for over a decade,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:28.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and Black Myth: Wukong,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:33.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I've been following them since their first public appearance until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:36.76,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,any harm to either side will make me very angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:40.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,MTJJ is unwise,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:43.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,while Game Science is as still as a mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:47.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,truly has great wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:50.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder that MTJJ worked in a big company before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:53.56,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,MTJJ said
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:57.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,he wanted to end this dispute with an article,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:19:00.54,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,this is because of his own double standards and sarcastic attitude towards employees,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:03.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and after coming out three times,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:07.35,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I don't think he found where his problem lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:10.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,this makes me extremely disappointed in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:13.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,But in the end, there's no smoke without fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:17.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,some people spread rumors,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:21.64,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,some people fan the flames,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:24.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,those who maliciously set the rhythm for Black Myth: Wukong,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:27.12,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,shouldn't they be the ones to receive the public's anger?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:30.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,But what we see is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:33.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,these people are still at large,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:35.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I am very angry about this reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:37.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but I can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:42.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I actually tried to use the opportunity of MTJJ's apology
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:47.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,to direct the anger towards those rumor-mongers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:52.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and not let them hide behind MTJJ and laugh anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:55.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,But unfortunately, MTJJ's sarcasm is too high,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:58.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,he directly controlled the entire forum,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:01.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,must first attack that sarcastic follower.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:03.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,What can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:06.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Some people accuse me of stirring up trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:08.22,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:10.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I can't accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:13.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Because from the beginning, everyone can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:17.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I've been putting out fires for MTJJ and Sun Gua.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:19.50,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Some people say I'm a victim,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:22.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I also don't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:25.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Although Sun Gua
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:28.80,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,did repost my remarks to her homepage,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:31.08,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but I actually welcome her doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:34.65,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Because only open discussion is beneficial to clarify the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:36.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,make it clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:37.91,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Her blocking me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.91,0:20:39.37,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,can only prove that she is in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:42.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,This wave of digging up old accounts is not only a great reversal drama,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:46.95,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but also evokes my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:51.04,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Next is what I call the long-buried truth in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:54.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I am a person who is not socially anxious but very self-enclosed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:58.92,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,The internet has been my spiritual haven since a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:03.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I have learned a lot of knowledge here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:07.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,seen all kinds of witty and humorous brainstorms,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:11.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,admired the extraordinary skills of people from all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:14.03,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I have gained a lot of happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:15.94,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and also gained a lot of strength
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:18.97,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,to face various difficulties in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.97,0:21:21.71,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,But what is the internet like now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:25.78,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I see more and more prejudice,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:27.77,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,more and more baseless accusations,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:30.39,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,more and more people have to wear armor,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:32.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,wear thicker and thicker armor,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:34.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but still receive more and more curses.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.40,0:21:38.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,The past golden age obviously can't come back overnight,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.81,0:21:42.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but I still want to regain
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:45.18,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the right to breathe freely on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:48.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,To return to the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:52.83,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I think we must unite to resist those extremists.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:55.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,This matter
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:21:58.75,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,must be the joint effort of everyone who participates in the internet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:00.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,to achieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:03.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,This time, we used magic to defeat magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:07.48,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,which is indeed satisfying,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.48,0:22:11.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but it accelerates the deterioration of the internet atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.25,0:22:14.24,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,As MTJJ himself said,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:17.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,making something out of nothing and escalating things
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.25,0:22:19.55,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,is indeed despicable,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.55,0:22:22.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but on the current internet,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:25.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,this trick is really effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.26,0:22:29.16,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I sincerely call for us to return to reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:32.72,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,return to kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.72,0:22:36.15,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,return to tolerance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.15,0:22:38.81,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Actually, up to this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.81,0:22:40.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I think it can end,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:42.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but some people might ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.66,0:22:45.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,what is my attitude towards gender equality?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:48.59,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,So I'll add another paragraph.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:51.58,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,My attitude is that since 1921 until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.58,0:22:53.63,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,since the founding of New China until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.63,0:22:57.26,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,we have been supporting women's equality in practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.26,0:23:01.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,women participating in labor and social activities,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:05.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the slogan that "women can hold up half the sky" has been passed down to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.23,0:23:09.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,We once had excellent female tractor drivers,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.23,0:23:11.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,excellent female workers,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.23,0:23:13.23,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,excellent female scientists,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.23,0:23:16.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,and now there are still countless excellent women
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:19.52,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,realizing their own value in various industries,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.52,0:23:23.00,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,contributing their own strength to the progress of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:26.61,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,What I support is the true gender equality behind this great cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:29.98,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Take myself as an example,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.98,0:23:33.70,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,because of the major I studied, I am surrounded by women who are more excellent than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:35.42,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,If I had any gender discrimination,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:37.40,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I would have been so angry that I would have died young long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.40,0:23:40.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Gender equality,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:42.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,in my understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:46.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,is to make gender irrelevant when it's irrelevant to the matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.46,0:23:48.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,not a topic of discussion,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.46,0:23:50.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,no one talks about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.46,0:23:52.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,whether you are male or female,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.46,0:23:54.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,you work more and get more,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.46,0:23:56.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,you work less and get less,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:58.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the standards are the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.46,0:24:00.46,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,the rules are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.46,0:24:02.66,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,And when things are related to gender,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.66,0:24:06.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,everyone acknowledges the objective differences between the two sexes,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.30,0:24:08.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,everyone complements each other's strengths,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.30,0:24:10.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,helps each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.30,0:24:12.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,with these as the standard,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.30,0:24:14.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I would like to ask everyone to think,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.30,0:24:18.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,where in the world is gender equality done better than here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.30,0:24:22.89,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Of course, our reality is still some distance away from true gender equality,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.89,0:24:26.45,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but gender equality is not achieved by unreasonable demands occupying three points,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.45,0:24:31.38,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,reasonable demands not letting go, and making trouble out of nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.38,0:24:35.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Some people,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.30,0:24:37.25,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,they shout equality in their mouths,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.25,0:24:39.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,but in fact, they want privileges.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.30,0:24:42.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,If these thugs get their way,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.30,0:24:46.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,those women who achieve success through their own efforts,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.30,0:24:49.60,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,aren't they the biggest victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.60,0:24:51.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,I absolutely do not allow such things to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.30,0:24:53.30,BottomCenter,,0,0,0,,Thank you all.
